SEE ALL THE BENEFITS OF MJFF MEMBERSHIP:
Click on image to view larger.
If you would like to mail a check, please make it out to CAJE/Miami Jewish Film Festival and address it to: Miami Jewish Film Festival, 4200 Biscayne Blvd, Miami, FL 33137. Checks sent from a foundation must be addressed to Center for the Advancement of Jewish Education, Inc.Â Employer Identification number: 59-0624373
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact the Miami Jewish Film Society office at 305-573-7304 or you can email us at
info@miamijewishfilmfestival.org
